{"tid":1908144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1928年香港報紙教你　甚麼是法治　不是楊鐵樑假貨","createTime":"2020-03-03T05:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T05:27:43.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1edbf1356eddeb87cda4ac64e6c8ea95348f403","tid":1908144,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663400593896015&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2663400593896015%26set%3Da.1403846723184748%26type%3D3&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=3c965beb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663400593896015&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n原來「教育青少年法治精神」、「具備法治意識，自發地遵守法律」係楊鐵樑呢條壽頭發明嘅。唔怪得講極法治都仲係被扭曲定義啦，要undo 30年嘅損害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m1hD7X7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm1hD7X7.jpg&h=30142fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663424780560263&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2663424780560263%26set%3Da.1403846723184748%26type%3D3&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=348019ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663424780560263&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n「法治精神」從來都係共產黨語嘅證據。<br />\n<br />\n1984賣豬仔之前，呢四隻字只出現過喺大公報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kxGhD5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkxGhD5H.jpg&h=d1cf7de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWan Leung Wong 法治係政府守法<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung 法治要共和才會的。日本人翻譯做共和，意思是分散力量的和平共存。單一力量只能自律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663843483851726&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2663843483851726%26set%3Da.1403846723184748%26type%3D3&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=ecf369f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663843483851726&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n輿論談及【法治】，最早最早見於1928年《工商日報》創辦人洪興錦寫嘅文章。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4BJzGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4BJzGe.jpg&h=5042abcc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}